com.yantra.yfc.rcp.foundation.containers.store.screens

Interface YRCStoreHeaderXP


  • public interface YRCStoreHeaderXP

    The SOPHeaderXP is the interface that needs to be implemented in order to extend the header panel of the Store Operations PCA's RCP screens.

      • setCustomPanel

        void setCustomPanel(org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Composite mainPnl)
        Description: setCustomPanel takes the base composite and paints the header panel on the left part of the header. The icon on the right of header cannot be changed using this. This method should be called before setTitle or setUserInfo. Because the labels have to be created first on the parent composite, only then can they be painted with text.
